## Changes Made

### 1. `internal/storage/storage.go` — Interface
Added `FlagExists` as the 4th method of `ReadOnlyFlagStore`:
```go
type ReadOnlyFlagStore interface {
    GetFlag(ctx context.Context, req ResourceRequest) (*flipt.Flag, error)
    ListFlags(ctx context.Context, req *ListRequest[NamespaceRequest]) (ResultSet[*flipt.Flag], error)
    CountFlags(ctx context.Context, ns NamespaceRequest) (uint64, error)
    FlagExists(ctx context.Context, req ResourceRequest) (bool, error)  // ← added
}
```
Because `FlagStore` embeds `ReadOnlyFlagStore` and `Store` embeds `FlagStore`, the method propagates to the full `storage.Store` interface automatically.

### 2. `internal/storage/fs/snapshot.go` — `*Snapshot`
```go
func (ss *Snapshot) FlagExists(ctx context.Context, req storage.ResourceRequest) (bool, error) {
    _, err := ss.GetFlag(ctx, req)
    if err != nil {
        if errs.AsMatch[errs.ErrNotFound](err) {
            return false, nil
        }
        return false, err
    }
    return true, nil
}
```

### 3. `internal/storage/sql/common/flag.go` — `*common.Store`
```go
func (s *Store) FlagExists(ctx context.Context, p storage.ResourceRequest) (bool, error) {
    _, err := s.GetFlag(ctx, p)
    if err != nil {
        if errs.AsMatch[errs.ErrNotFound](err) {
            return false, nil
        }
        return false, err
    }
    return true, nil
}
```

### 4. `internal/storage/fs/store.go` — `*fs.Store`
```go
func (s *Store) FlagExists(ctx context.Context, req storage.ResourceRequest) (exists bool, err error) {
    return exists, s.viewer.View(ctx, req.Reference, func(ss storage.ReadOnlyStore) error {
        exists, err = ss.FlagExists(ctx, req)
        return err
    })
}
```
Placed immediately after `GetFlag`, following the exact same `viewer.View` delegation pattern used by every other read method.

### 5. `internal/common/store_mock.go` — `*StoreMock`
```go
func (m *StoreMock) FlagExists(ctx context.Context, flag storage.ResourceRequest) (bool, error) {
    args := m.Called(ctx, flag)
    return args.Get(0).(bool), args.Error(1)
}
```

### Types that inherit automatically (no change needed)
- **`sql/sqlite.Store`**, **`sql/postgres.Store`**, **`sql/mysql.Store`** — all embed `*common.Store`, inheriting `FlagExists` via Go struct promotion.
- **`cache.Store`** — embeds the `storage.Store` interface field, delegating `FlagExists` to the wrapped store automatically.

